# Docker rebuild (weekly-meal-planner)

After **any** code or config change that should show up in the containerized app, rebuild and restart the stack from the project root (`sdd/weekly-meal-planner`):

```bash
docker compose build && docker compose up -d
```

Use `docker compose build --no-cache` if the image seems stale. Do not skip this step when the user cares about the Docker deployment.
